    "causal_summary": "Packet 069 now has Motion.dev peer references and manual playbook coverage, but it lacks a repeatable way to ask multiple AI runtimes how they would route the same sk-code scenarios. Without a deterministic prompt and runner harness, cross-CLI routing audits depend on ad hoc transcripts and cannot reliably catch misroutes across Codex, Copilot, Gemini, and OpenCode.",
